Developer Terms of Use
des:
This skill enables users to query information about Online Registry and its conferences. Online Registry is a well-approved conference and submission management system which covers a huge feature set in a single tool. With this skill, it is possible to ask for important dates and deadlines of conferences handled by Online Registry.

For more information, visit our product page at https://www.online-registry.net/
Online Registry is being developed by webtek.at
